---
title: Homemade Vegetable-Packed Calzone with Spring Mix and Italian Vinaigrette
description: We swapped out pizza dough for rich and flaky puff pastry. It creates the perfect crisp vessel for our bell pepper, leek and cheese filling! It's oh so ooey gooey and tasty!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/calzones-maison-aux-legumes-432219e5.jpg
